&lt;p&gt;Roessner &amp;amp; Co. is a strategic design firm that specializes in creating annual reports for international clients. &amp;nbsp;They depend on reliable access to e-mail every day when communicating with their customers. Roessner &amp;amp; Co. trusts Elix to provide business critical hosting services for their email and corporate website. &amp;nbsp;Elix migrated their e-mail services from a legacy POP3 solution to a cloud based platform based on Microsoft Exchange 2010, SharePoint 2010, and a custom content management layer for their public website.&lt;/p&gt;
